[import](1.lg)
> Welcome Phrase template
> LG runtime will pick a text value from the one-of collection list at random.
# wPhrase
- Salut
- Bonjour
- Hé, c’est

> Using a template in another template
> Sometimes the bot will say 'Hi' and other times it will say 'Hi :)'
# welcome-user(userName)
- ${wPhrase()} ${userName} :)

> Using entity references
# welcome
- IF: ${userName}
    - ${welcome-user(userName)}
- ELSE:
    - ${welcome-user('DongLei')}



# ShowAlarm(alarm)
- ${alarm.time} À ${alarm.date}

# ShowAlarmsWithForeach
- IF: ${count(alarms) == 1}
   - Vous avez une alarme ${ShowAlarm(alarms[0])}
- ELSEIF: ${count(alarms) == 2}
  - Vous avez ${count(alarms)} Alarmes ${join(foreach(alarms, x, ShowAlarm(x)), ', ', ' and ')}
- ELSE:
  - Vous n’avez pas d’alarmes

# ShowAlarmsWithLgTemplate
- IF: ${count(alarms) == 1}
   - Vous avez une alarme ${ShowAlarm(alarms[0])}
- ELSEIF: ${count(alarms) == 2}
